**LIX Calculator:** https://www.skolverket.se/undervisning/grundskoleutbildning/sprak-laes-och-skrivutveckling/skriftlig-framstallning/lixtal

**Steps:**
1. Count the number of words: 102
2. Count the number of sentences: 7
3. Count the number of words with more than 6 letters: 34
4. Calculate LIX using the formula: LIX = (WordsWith6+ > / Words) x (Sentences / Words) x 100
5. Plug in the values: LIX = (34 / 102) X (7 / 102) X 100 = 26.24

**Result:**
LIX=26.24